.TH "drm_hdmi_infoframe_set_hdr_metadata" 9 "drm_hdmi_infoframe_set_hdr_metadata" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_hdmi_infoframe_set_hdr_metadata \- fill an HDMI DRM infoframe with HDR metadata from userspace
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" drm_hdmi_infoframe_set_hdr_metadata
.BI "(struct hdmi_drm_infoframe *frame "  ","
.BI "const struct drm_connector_state *conn_state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "frame" 12
HDMI DRM infoframe
.IP "conn_state" 12
Connector state containing HDR metadata
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or a negative error code on failure.
